data.description: 8K BUYER CONCESSION!!! Discover the stunning Rutledge plan by Mungo Homes, an exquisite all-brick beauty, built in 2020! Step into a 2-story foyer, flanked by a formal dining room boasting a coffered ceiling & versatile living room which may be utilized as a home office. The kitchen, a culinary dream, showcases crisp white cabinetry, granite countertops, spacious island with seating, gas cooktop, stainless steel appliances &  walk-in corner pantry. Enjoy the eat-in space overlooking the backyard or relax in the grand living room, seamlessly flowing into a screened porch. Hand-scraped engineered hardwood floors exude warmth throughout the main living areas. A large bedroom with an ensuite bath completes the main floor. Upstairs, indulge in the huge owner’s suite with 2 walk-in closets, a storage closet, and a cozy sitting area. The luxurious bath features double vanities, a tiled shower, and a freestanding tub. Two bedrooms share a Jack-and-Jill bath, while an additional bedroom provides flexibility. Convenient laundry room upstairs. The spacious media room/flex space opens onto a charming covered balcony. With a 3-car garage and over half an acre lot, this home is a true gem! Don't miss out on this unparalleled opportunity! Contact our team today for a showing!
